{"comments":"Carousel Effects — Visual effects applied to slides based on position.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nEffects are pure functions: SlidePosition -> CSS properties.\nEach effect can be independently enabled/disabled via toggles.\nEffects compose — multiple can be active simultaneously.\n\n## Effect Categories\n\n**Opacity Effects**: Fade inactive slides\n**Transform Effects**: Scale, rotate, translate, skew\n**Filter Effects**: Blur, grayscale, saturate, brightness\n**Material Effects**: Reflections, shadows, glow\n**3D Effects**: Perspective, depth, parallax layers\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Carousel.Types (SlidePosition)\n- Schema atoms (Color, Dimension, etc.)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[132,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Carousel/Effects.purs","start":[132,3]},"title":"EffectOpacity"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[133,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Carousel/Effects.purs","start":[133,3]},"title":"EffectScale"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[134,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Carousel/Effects.purs","start":[134,3]},"title":"EffectBlur"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[135,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Carousel/Effects.purs","start":[135,3]},"title":"EffectRotation"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[136,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Carousel/Effects.purs","start":[136,3]},"title":"EffectReflection"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[137,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Carousel/Effects.purs","start":[137,3]},"title":"EffectP